   slạmh ygẖmrnạ ḥḍwrh ạ̉kyd
   hw lnạ ạ̹lhnạ ạlḍạmn ạlwḥyd

[V2]
 2- lạ sẖyʾ fy ḥyạtnạ ạ̉kyd
 fqd tʿlm ạlạ̹nsạn ạ̉n ykyd
 ydbr ạlmkạỷd wyktẖr ạlthdyd

[V3]
 3- lạ sẖyʾ fy ḥyạtnạ ydwm
